name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 10 – Eager Eagles, Son Dating, and Uncomfortable Bosses

content.html:
Dear Internet, On this week’s show, we have to wild stories from the internet to tell you about. We explore living with wild birds, the mindfield that is letting your adult children date other adults, and bosses that may or may not be ministers. We are a new show, and would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Cast of Thrones. Sincerely, The coHosts- Nick Bristow, Jennifer Cheek, Michael DiMauro, and Tim Lanning! Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!

By Dear Internet
